    Revision:
      pyosd--dev--1.0--patch-14

    * cast totalCapacity as a float, to avoid erroneous "battery at 0%"
      messages
    
    * derive the last full battery capacity if available
    
    * don't rely on unix directory ordering - assume BAT0.
    
    * code tidy-up.

